            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E6%9B%B4%E9%80%82%E5%AE%9C%E5%BF%83%E8%A1%80%E7%AE%A1%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E6%9B%B4%E9%80%82%E5%AE%9C%E5%BF%83%E8%A1%80%E7%AE%A1%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#南方更适宜心血管疾病患者生活#</span></a>？】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E4%BA%BA%E5%86%AC%E5%A4%A9%E5%8E%BB%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E8%BF%87%E5%86%AC%E4%BC%9A%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E4%BA%BA%E5%86%AC%E5%A4%A9%E5%8E%BB%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E8%BF%87%E5%86%AC%E4%BC%9A%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#北方人冬天去南方过冬会更好吗#</span></a> ？医生认为，南方空气湿润、温度适宜，比较适合心血管疾病患者生活。但心血管疾病患者如果适应了南方的温度，再突然回到北方，则可能会有不适应的情况。特别是有基础疾病的老年人，更要小心👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YShtc7" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
