            <title><![CDATA[【🚭#胃食管反流竟与吸烟有关# 】我们平常说的“烧心”，其实是胃食管反流的一种常见症状。除了饮食，吸烟也会影响胃食管反流导致胃酸！吸烟过程中，产生的有...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🚭<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%83%E9%A3%9F%E7%AE%A1%E5%8F%8D%E6%B5%81%E7%AB%9F%E4%B8%8E%E5%90%B8%E7%83%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%83%E9%A3%9F%E7%AE%A1%E5%8F%8D%E6%B5%81%E7%AB%9F%E4%B8%8E%E5%90%B8%E7%83%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胃食管反流竟与吸烟有关#</span></a> 】我们平常说的“烧心”，其实是胃食管反流的一种常见症状。除了饮食，吸烟也会影响胃食管反流导致胃酸！吸烟过程中，产生的有害物质会通过血液运输到全身，可能对胃和消化道的黏膜造成伤害，导致贲门松弛。此外，吸烟与胃癌、食管癌的发生也有密切关系👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5001497339953190" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hmtj5n18dtj20u01hcgo8.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/anZnB2UYlx08cxLlbVw4010412005MSY0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708420531&amp;ssig=d5ZgYieHNw&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/NrnwuhLSlx08cxLl5je8010412003q7Y0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708420531&amp;ssig=jFNuyE74fi&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/kmEjsEK2lx08cxLl3DqE010412001RZ50E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708420531&amp;ssig=S8jcC1hUH5&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5001497339953190" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
